26
00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:39.039
<i>MAN 1: Start talking.</i>

27
00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:40.799
<i>MAN 2: I'm not sure if we're on the air.</i>

28
00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:42.919
<i>This is a series of explosions...</i>

29
00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:45.919
<i>WOMAN 1: We're being told this is a major incident.</i>

30
00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:47.999
<i>The emergency is a major incident.</i>

31
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.719
<i>MAN 3: ...bright lights and an orange glow.</i>

32
00:00:49.720 --> 00:00:51.759
<i>WOMAN 2: That was the moment the meteor hit.</i>

33
00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:54.839
<i>MAN 4: It does now appear to be a major attack.</i>

34
00:00:54.840 --> 00:00:56.959
<i>WOMAN 3: Since they landed outside Hamburg five years ago...</i>

35
00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:59.213
<i>they have steadily advanced across Europe.</i>

36
00:00:59.239 --> 00:01:01.359
<i>We've suffered millions of casualties.</i>

37
00:01:01.360 --> 00:01:05.279
<i>The evacuation of key government officials continuing.</i>

38
00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:07.119
<i>MAN 5: Nothing has stopped their advance.</i>

39
00:01:07.120 --> 00:01:09.439
<i>MAN 6: In human costs. the Europeans have paid the highest price.</i>

40
00:01:09.440 --> 00:01:12.959
<i>They have the ability to mimic and even anticipate our actions.</i>

41
00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.999
<i>BRIGHAM: If we do not defeat them in France...</i>

42
00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.199
<i>we'll be fighting them in London then New York. then Tokyo.</i>

43
00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:19.439
[CROWD YELLING]

44
00:01:19.440 --> 00:01:21.159
<i>All of humanity's at stake.</i>

45
00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:23.679
<i>MAN 7: After five years we finally have a victory.</i>

46
00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:26.239
<i>WOMAN 4: These pictures are just in from Verdun.</i>

47
00:01:26.240 --> 00:01:28.519
<i>MAN 8: One of the striking things was how low casualties were...</i>

48
00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:30.359
<i>and how little damage...</i>

49
00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:33.003
<i>MAN 9: We have seen a stunning victory here today.</i>

50
00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:37.679
<i>HILL: How do you convince people that this is a fight that can be won?</i>

51
00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:39.759
<i>This is an alien invasion in a global war.</i>

52
00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:42.399
<i>With the new jacket technology and limited training...</i>

53
00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:45.089
<i>we've been able to create super-soldiers.</i>

54
00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.599
<i>Look at Rita Vrataski. the Angel of Verdun.</i>

55
00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:50.319
<i>WOMAN 5: They're calling her the Angel of Verdun.</i>

56
00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:52.839
<i>She is seen as the new hope for this war.</i>

57
00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:54.279
<i>WOMAN 6: It's extraordinary.</i>

58
00:01:54.280 --> 00:01:56.759
<i>With the new jacket technology and limited training...</i>

59
00:01:56.760 --> 00:01:58.999
<i>Rita Vrataski was able to kill...</i>

60
00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:01.039
<i>hundreds of mimics on only her first day.</i>

61
00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:03.279
<i>MAN 10: Is the tide of this war changing?</i>

62
00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:06.719
<i>WOMAN 7: The Army attribute this success to a revolutionary new technology:</i>

63
00:02:06.720 --> 00:02:08.519
<i>The Exosuit jacket.</i>

64
00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:10.759
[PEOPLE SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

65
00:02:10.760 --> 00:02:14.319
<i>She was able to kill hundreds of mimics on only her first day in combat.</i>

66
00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:16.919
<i>Imagine an army of Rita Vrataskis.</i>

67
00:02:16.920 --> 00:02:20.879
<i>BURNETT: We're holding them back at the English Channel. but for how long?</i>

68
00:02:20.880 --> 00:02:22.388
<i>MAN 11: This is dangerous talk.</i>

69
00:02:22.414 --> 00:02:24.479
<i>People are suspicious about this invasion.</i>

70
00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:26.079
<i>MAN 12: Over 17 nations have joined the United Defense Force...</i>

71
00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:27.848
<i>which hopes to push them back.</i>

72
00:02:27.874 --> 00:02:29.439
<i>We've got them contained.</i>

73
00:02:29.440 --> 00:02:32.479
<i>And with this new technology. we're gonna defeat them.</i>

74
00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:36.479
<i>Operation Downfall is going to be the largest mechanized invasion in history.</i>

75
00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:39.143
<i>We will be victorious. We fight.</i>

76
00:02:39.169 --> 00:02:40.832
<i>That's what we do.</i>

77
00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:48.074
